{"pageProps":{"mdBlocks":[{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-813e-a3cf-cd6fd697934c","parent":"今回は、既存のテーブルを後から編集する方法を説明します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81b9-bf37-ddd7256f4dd5","type":"heading_2","parent":"## テーブルの編集方法","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81d3-a856-fdebba378396","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81be-862a-c27062cfe078","parent":"テーブルを編集する方法を見ましょう。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8155-b26b-c95126b521e5","type":"callout","parent":"> テーブルを編集するSQL文  \n> ```sql  \n> ALTER TABLE テーブル名 編集内容  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8140-a6d7-c878be375a95","type":"code","parent":"```sql\nALTER TABLE テーブル名 編集内容\n```","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8110-b760-f63b51c1f219","parent":"テーブルを編集するには、`ALTER TABLE`を使います。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8115-935a-c44db9159e3f","parent":"編集内容の部分には、カラム名の変更、カラムの追加、カラムの削除のいずれかが入ります。\n順番に見ていきましょう。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8118-bbdf-c94490286f0a","type":"heading_2","parent":"## カラム名の変更","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8170-b463-da2d0e7a1ccf","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81e8-863d-d26e535b1d52","type":"callout","parent":"> カラム名の変更  \n> ```sql  \n> ALTER TABLE テーブル名 RENAME COLUMN 古いカラム名 TO 新しいカラム名  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81c0-bbe0-ca799f240821","type":"code","parent":"```sql\nALTER TABLE テーブル名 RENAME COLUMN 古いカラム名 TO 新しいカラム名\n```","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8137-baa2-cd710ef31306","parent":"既存のカラムの名前を変更するには`RENAME COLUMN`を使います。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81c4-ad94-f5a069b5b964","type":"callout","parent":"> 例：`person`テーブルのカラム`name`を`full_name`に変更する  \n> ```sql  \n> ALTER TABLE person RENAME COLUMN name TO full_name  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8144-8f6c-fe74fb997184","type":"code","parent":"```sql\nALTER TABLE person RENAME COLUMN name TO full_name\n```","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-819f-a458-c3d7f7f4129c","parent":"この例では、`person`テーブルの`name`カラムを`full_name`という名前に変更します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-816d-810a-d15dc62ba2f2","type":"heading_2","parent":"## カラムの追加","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-815d-857e-eb4144c165e0","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81d5-acc7-e62dd60a219a","type":"callout","parent":"> カラムの追加  \n> ```sql  \n> ALTER TABLE テーブル名 ADD 新しいカラム名 データ型  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-811d-9cab-c76c7c02653e","type":"code","parent":"```sql\nALTER TABLE テーブル名 ADD 新しいカラム名 データ型\n```","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8172-a2d4-e709ae98e04f","parent":"カラムを追加するには`ADD`を使用します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81de-8dd6-f0d6fd209c57","type":"callout","parent":"> 例：`person`テーブルに`job`カラムを追加する  \n> ```sql  \n> ALTER TABLE person ADD job TEXT  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81a8-aa16-ff6db8f280da","type":"code","parent":"```sql\nALTER TABLE person ADD job TEXT\n```","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8162-802c-cc1b68a42ada","parent":"この例では、`person`テーブルに、新たなカラム`job`を追加しています。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8143-b831-f9d1f0312e94","type":"heading_2","parent":"## カラムの削除","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-815b-9f67-c9b0e5817f4b","type":"divider","parent":"---","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-811c-958e-fffea910a345","type":"callout","parent":"> カラムの削除  \n> ```sql  \n> ALTER TABLE テーブル名 DROP COLUMN カラム名  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81c7-995e-d7e90ec17620","type":"code","parent":"```sql\nALTER TABLE テーブル名 DROP COLUMN カラム名\n```","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-812e-a4b9-d9ea6d780ca7","parent":"カラムを削除するには、`DROP COLUMN`を使用します。","children":[]},{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8133-919b-d254c54a876d","type":"callout","parent":"> 例：personテーブルのageカラムを削除する  \n> ```sql  \n> ALTER TABLE person DROP COLUMN age  \n> ```","children":[{"blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-814b-9585-cea19f89a157","type":"code","parent":"```sql\nALTER TABLE person DROP COLUMN age\n```","children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-81aa-a442-e0167056b02d","parent":"この例では、`person`テーブルの`age`カラムを削除します。","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-816f-8bdc-c6c273bc54fd","parent":"","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8103-89ae-fe016bd12075","parent":"次→[**CRUD操作を使い回せるようにしよう**](/posts/post/19d2297f-7a72-80e3-9222-fee4cd48536f/19d2297f-7a72-81d5-b81a-d1366e7bafac)","children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","blockId":"19d2297f-7a72-8141-b0b8-dc2579626ad0","parent":"","children":[]}],"pageNavs":[{"title":"Home","id":"/posts"},{"title":"基礎班カリキュラム","id":"/posts/course/basic"},{"title":"後期","id":"/posts/course/後期"},{"title":"データベース基礎","id":"/posts/post/19d2297f-7a72-80e3-9222-fee4cd48536f"},{"title":"テーブルの編集","id":"/posts/post/19d2297f-7a72-80e3-9222-fee4cd48536f19d2297f-7a72-815c-8bd9-df9b6d31f648"}],"parentTitle":"データベース基礎","childNavs":[{"title":"データベースとは","id":"19d2297f-7a72-8167-ac83-da8e0ace31a5","child":true},{"title":"Pythonでデータベースを扱うためのライブラリ","id":"19d2297f-7a72-8190-8632-dfe77e08f562","child":true},{"title":"データベースとの接続とテーブルの作成","id":"19d2297f-7a72-8170-a321-daff5ba9bc0a","child":true},{"title":"データの保存(Create)","id":"19d2297f-7a72-819d-8ecc-ded1c97afcc0","child":true},{"title":"データの取得(Read)","id":"19d2297f-7a72-81ae-ab43-f15cda8b9b88","child":true},{"title":"データの編集(Update)","id":"19d2297f-7a72-8165-b201-cd77e1e2d2f2","child":true},{"title":"データの削除(Delete)","id":"19d2297f-7a72-812f-8685-d8d24d05ae5f","child":true},{"title":"テーブルの編集","id":"19d2297f-7a72-815c-8bd9-df9b6d31f648","child":true},{"title":"CRUD操作を使い回せるようにしよう","id":"19d2297f-7a72-81d5-b81a-d1366e7bafac","child":true},{"title":"マイグレーション","id":"19d2297f-7a72-812d-bffe-f90403d06872","child":true},{"title":"カラムの属性","id":"19d2297f-7a72-81